sections.heading: Sections; supplementary to existing law
sections.text: Sections 16-801 to 16-811 are supplementary to existing statutes relating to cities of the first class and confer upon such cities powers not heretofore granted.SourceLaws 1955, c. 35, ยง 11, p. 147.
